commentTextItems.html: onto the frontfoot and drives it down to long-on for a run, that was a very simple finish to the game
tossed up, goes for drive but gets beaten and keeper wipes the bails but not-out
onto the pads, flicks it to short mid-wicket
onto the frontfoot and driven to long-on for a run
onto the frontfoot and drives it back to the bowler
onto the backfoot and guides it towards point and fielder stops it

headshotImage.caption: Ahmed Raza player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Ahmed Raza player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: onto the backfoot and cuts it to point for a quick run
tossed up, drives it but straight to cover fielder
onto the frontfoot and driven down to long-on for a run
quicker on leg, looks to drag it to sqaure leg but gets hit on the pad
onto the frontfoot and drives it down to long-off for a run
down the leg, sweeps it firmly and past the fielder at square leg for a boundary

headshotImage.caption: Ahmed Raza player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Ahmed Raza player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: onto the frontfoot and blocks it
onto the backfoot and pushed to point, fielder throws at the non-striker end out of no purpose and gives away an extra run for over throw
down the leg, nudges it fine to fine leg for a triple and reaches his fifty
tossed up, takes a long stride and blocks it
tossed up, drives it to cover fielder
quicker ball, blocks it of the backfoot
